1
00:01:19,920 --> 00:01:21,000
When Lu Jingheng thinks

2
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,600
you're no longer useful,

3
00:01:23,320 --> 00:01:25,000
he will cast you aside like an old shoe.

4
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,160
My business with him

5
00:01:26,600 --> 00:01:29,130
doesn't need Second Young Master's concern.

6
00:01:29,800 --> 00:01:30,680
Some things,

7
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,479
even if you forget,

8
00:01:34,759 --> 00:01:36,490
someone will remember for you.

9
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:38,640
As for the past,

10
00:01:38,880 --> 00:01:41,410
it's up to me whether it's worth remembering.

11
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:44,570
Instead of worrying about other people's business,

12
00:01:44,800 --> 00:01:47,800
Second Young Master should manage his own ambitions.

13
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:54,400
Miss.

14
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:56,640
This is the feedback form filled out by that gentleman.

15
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:57,440
Thank you.

16
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:08,720
It's not him.

17
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,520
All that for nothing.

18
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:15,560
I gave her a chance.

19
00:02:16,480 --> 00:02:17,760
I gave her a chance.

20
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,520
She didn't want it.

21
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:41,160
There was something wrong with that drink.

22
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,360
Miss, you're drunk.

23
00:02:47,440 --> 00:02:48,600
We'll take you home.

24
00:02:48,600 --> 00:02:49,730
Let us take you home.

25
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,360
Let us take you home.

26
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,480
Who are you?

27
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:40,000
Zhixia, are you alright?

28
00:04:41,280 --> 00:04:42,610
Shen Zhixia, sit still.

29
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,520
Sit still.

30
00:04:52,840 --> 00:04:53,640
Wake up.

31
00:04:54,680 --> 00:04:55,480
Sit still.

32
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:03,000
Leave me alone.

33
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,200
I'll go get a doctor.

34
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:26,800
Don't go.

35
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,880
I feel much better.

36
00:06:30,640 --> 00:06:32,000
You can barely stand.

37
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:37,200
Don't go. I'm scared.

38
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,060
I just need some sleep.

39
00:06:58,760 --> 00:07:00,760
I'll be fine after a sleep.

40
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:44,450
Why did you make me wait so long?

41
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,960
Do you want to die?

42
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:49,880
Where are the photos?

43
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,680
S-Second Young Master.

44
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,840
I didn't get it done.

45
00:07:53,320 --> 00:07:54,840
Lu Jingheng suddenly appeared

46
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:56,000
and took her away.

47
00:07:58,000 --> 00:07:58,800
Trash!

48
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,650
Tell me, what was so difficult?

49
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:05,800
What was so difficult?

50
00:08:05,800 --> 00:08:06,520
I found the person,

51
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,160
and I drugged her.

52
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,320
You just needed to take a few photos.

53
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:09,580
What was so difficult?

54
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:11,560
Go to hell, all of you!

55
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,250
Lu Jingxi, what's the rush?

56
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:27,400
Why the rush?

57
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:31,560
The show has just begun.

58
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,480
I won't let it end so easily.

59
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,700
Get up if you're awake.

60
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:15,260
The effects of yesterday's medicine should have worn off.

61
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,280
Good morning.

62
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:26,280
Why did you go looking for Lu Jingxi yesterday?

63
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:33,720
Just because of some things from the past.

64
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,440
Why couldn't you come to me about the past,

65
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:39,720
instead of insisting on finding Lu Jingxi?

66
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:41,160
I can't just tell him

67
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:42,040
that I was trying to find

68
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:45,370
the person who corresponded with the original host, right?

69
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:47,680
Just some trivial matters.

70
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,560
Trivial?

71
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:50,920
Shen Zhixia.

72
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:53,960
We made a three-point pact.

73
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:57,090
The dignity of the Lu family is my bottom line.

74
00:09:57,560 --> 00:10:00,360
Did you have a relationship with Lu Jingxi before?

75
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,880
Do you think if you don't say it,

76
00:10:04,880 --> 00:10:06,680
others won't know about you two?

77
00:10:08,600 --> 00:10:10,200
You'd better think carefully

78
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,060
how to explain to the whole world.

79
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:33,580
[Wealthy Family Melodrama T]

80
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:32,040
[1 hour ago]

81
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:32,040
[Jiu Jiu Jiu Jiu]

82
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,400
Hello, ma'am.

83
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:01,480
Mr. Wen doesn't like being photographed.

84
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,320
Mr. Wen.

85
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:11,210
He is Wen Zhuocheng, the founder of Wenji.

86
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:13,960
Over the years, the Wen family hasn't just been in the food industry.

87
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:16,200
They have even invested in media and sports.

88
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,960
They have expanded their business a lot.

89
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,920
In terms of family wealth,

90
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:22,720
I think they are second only to the Lu family.

91
00:11:22,840 --> 00:11:23,960
So handsome.

92
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:43,120
Have you been waiting long?

93
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:43,780
Not really.

94
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,240
You didn't go to the office.

95
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:47,200
Why are you playing the piano in your own restaurant?

96
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,640
I'm just thinking of you.

97
00:11:48,640 --> 00:11:50,600
The recent news has been bothering you.

98
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:53,000
So I played a couple of tunes to cheer you up.

99
00:11:53,160 --> 00:11:54,760
I saw the trending searches.

100
00:11:55,000 --> 00:11:57,320
You don't like Miss Shen anyway.

101
00:11:57,400 --> 00:11:58,920
Now that there's a scandal,

102
00:11:58,920 --> 00:12:00,400
you might as well just divorce her.

103
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:01,600
It'd be a clean break.

104
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:06,080
The news has already affected

105
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:07,360
the company's stock price.

106
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:09,220
Divorce won't solve the problem.

107
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:12,920
So, what's your plan?

108
00:12:12,920 --> 00:12:14,520
I heard Wen Shuyi returned

109
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:16,360
and took over your family's Zhuoyue PR.

110
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:18,320
So I want you to connect us

111
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:20,720
and see if she's willing to help out.

112
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,200
Shuyi just returned.

113
00:12:23,160 --> 00:12:24,600
But she just finalized her divorce.

114
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:26,120
She still has things to sort out.

115
00:12:26,120 --> 00:12:27,680
We haven't seen each other recently.

116
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:29,560
So I'm not sure if she has time.

117
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:30,930
We grew up together.

118
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:33,480
Just ask her directly if you need anything.

119
00:12:34,920 --> 00:12:35,680
Mr. Lu.

120
00:12:35,720 --> 00:12:36,920
The family just called,

121
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:38,680
saying Madam is making things difficult for the young madam.

122
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:39,680
What should we do?

123
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:43,480
Ignore her.

124
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:56,360
I have things to do. Talk to you later.

